Ranger Help for: echo
=====================

SYNTAX:      echo
USAGE:       Underground only
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     20
SKILL TYPE:  cartography

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to use a sonar-like technique underground,
sending out a sound and listening to the echoes to detect creatures in
adjacent rooms. The results report what creatures are nearby and in
which direction they can be found. This skill only works in underground
terrain. The accuracy depends on the Ranger's perception and skill
level. Echo is invaluable for navigating dangerous underground areas.
